  3.9682462723778477`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"d2a3926b-a82e-4da9-a893-\
ce096b5d6a50"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
1 = Input, 
2 = Just inside cavity near front mirror heading toward back mirror,
3 = Incident on back mirror
4 = Inside cavity near back mirror heading toward front mirror,
5 = Incident on front mirror (from the inside of the cavity)
6 = Reflected off front mirror,
7 = Transmitted through back mirror,

Columns are where the nth field is contributing to other fields,
Rows are where the nth field is receiving its fields from.\
\>", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.818573127079982*^9, 3.818573227085968*^9}, {
  3.818573278448423*^9, 3.818573355202489*^9}, {3.903107198895258*^9, 
